{"tid":1224363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭強調並非撤回條例草案，有關堵塞漏洞的工作會繼續進行。","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:18:54.000Z","uid":81783,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be8671face91f4b68806a1ad45decf0006cf4391","tid":1224363,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"大家睇重點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2019464-港聞-政府高層深夜急召會議+林鄭料今宣布暫緩修例\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2019464-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E6%80%A5%E5%8F%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%2B%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=ea4d520e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2019464-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E6%80%A5%E5%8F%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%2B%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B&h=38039d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2019464-港聞-政府高層深夜急召會議+林鄭料今宣布暫緩修例</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　（星島日報報道）政府原定在今年七月前完成《逃犯條例》修訂草案審議，惹來反對派連番發動遊行示威阻撓，甚至釀成暴力衝突。據悉，專責香港事務的中央港澳協調小組組長韓正近日南下深圳，並曾與特首林鄭月娥商討事件。而林鄭在衡量各種因素後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">決定暫緩修例，重新諮詢</span></span>。林鄭昨晚深夜召開全體司局長會議，商討有關決定，並會在今早會晤全體建制派議員交代決定及作出解釋，然後即會向公眾作出宣布。消息人士表示，今次決定是希望有關《逃犯條例》的修訂能夠回歸理性，讓政府有時間聽取民意，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">強調並非撤回條例草案，有關堵塞漏洞的工作會繼續進行</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">屌你老母即是暫緩一星期又得，一個月又得，<br />\n或者用另一個名既條例去堵塞漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚賤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特登講d可有可無既野，然後想坤人聽日唔好出黎<br />\n<br />\n然後聽日搞事就話都已經暫緩，你地仲搞事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依條八婆簡直仆街到頂點</span></span>"},{"pid":"56e130a168dcf415b21255883f649f14590d15bc","tid":1224363,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死八婆 屌你老味<br />\n香港人話要永久撤回呀</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"68c95b51bd7888aba09d743f47d320605ea069b1","tid":1224363,"uid":221265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"仲有鬼係諮詢<br />\n<br />\n轉頭又叫啲周融做簽名假民意話主流撐修例"},{"pid":"fab71290ada9b52eb502a5d386ef882ced9ccc32","tid":1224363,"uid":89200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"睇穿晒佢套路 奸撚過689 陰濕閪"},{"pid":"268c49cdaa34c9fc5d491f7f479a0855db6af0b2","tid":1224363,"uid":19278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBLMsTc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBLMsTc.jpg&h=2611045d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"985fd47b6253c9ad2a1c0a2e7ca1b00a37a90f4c","tid":1224363,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敵退我進</span></strong></span><br />\n不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bab103d4b5bdfa0ac8459e1743f74c885884e4","tid":1224363,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"暫你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633290334cecdb10047dc661442105383